	<p><strong>About this site</strong><br/>
	This site has been created with standards-rich HTML5, CSS3, JS, PHP, AJAX, website scrapes and Google API's. Images were created in Photoshop but some are also being resized on the fly. Text is set in Papyrus and Georgia.</p>
